### 2. Mobile "Shop by Age" Carousel
Convert the grid of age circles into a swipeable carousel on mobile devices to save vertical space.

#### [MODIFY] [styles.css](file:///d:/Projects/mindfuels-master/styles.css)
- Update `.age-sides` within a mobile media query (`@media (max-width: 768px)`) to use `display: flex`, `overflow-x: auto`, `scroll-snap-type: x mandatory`, and hide the scrollbar (`::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }`).
- Update `.age-card` on mobile to use `flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 15px)` and `scroll-snap-align: start` for smooth snapping behavior.

---

### 3. Premium Homepage Upgrades
Enhance the heading and "Shop All" button to look high-end.

#### [MODIFY] [styles.css](file:///d:/Projects/mindfuels-master/styles.css)
- **Headings (`.bestsellers-title`, `.age-title`)**: Apply a subtle, elegant text gradient (e.g., deep indigo to rich purple) and a refined font weight to make them stand out as premium elements.
- **Button (`.shop-all-btn`)**: Redesign with a dynamic gradient background, a soft box-shadow, and a smooth hover animation that scales the button slightly and enhances the gradient colors.

