### 4. Product Page Filters Fix
Allow users to combine filters to narrow down products effectively.

#### [MODIFY] [script.js](file:///d:/Projects/mindfuels-master/script.js)
- Locate the `change` event listener attached to the filter checkboxes.
- Remove the block of code that enforces single-selection (which loops through all checkboxes and sets `otherCb.checked = false`).
- Keep the `renderProducts()` call so the grid updates instantly when multiple filters are selected.

