### 5. Homepage Mobile Navbar "Shop" Icon
Replace the mobile search icon on the homepage.

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///d:/Projects/mindfuels-master/index.html)
- Add a new "Shop" icon link (e.g., a storefront or shopping bag SVG) next to the search wrapper.
- Add CSS utility classes to hide the search wrapper on mobile and show the new Shop icon on mobile.

#### [MODIFY] [styles.css](file:///d:/Projects/mindfuels-master/styles.css)
- Add `@media (max-width: 768px)` rules to toggle the visibility of the new Shop icon and the existing Search icon specifically for the homepage context.

